episodes.title: TBS | Police: Quiboloy picked victims from broken families
episodes.description:
#TheBigStory | Davao City Police Chief PCol. Hansel Marantan said that five victims have come forward after being allegedly sexually abused by Kingdom of Jesus Christ leader Apollo Quiboloy. 

Marantan added that there are at least 15 more individuals who also need to be rescued from KOJC.

episodes.title: TBS | Torreon: ISAFP pushed for Quiboloy's arrest inside KOJC compound
episodes.description:
#TheBigStory | KOJC's legal counsel, Atty. Israelito Torreon, revealed that they have been in coordination with the Intelligence Service of the Armed Forces of the Philippines (ISAFP) since August regarding Quiboloy's surrender.

Torreon said that ISAFP insisted that Quiboloy should be arrested within the KOJC compound.

Quiboloy only re-entered through a “south gate” after their request was granted.
